{"tid":2227680,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[本地遊] 抓住夏天的尾巴, 去荃灣大曹石澗Chill下","createTime":"2020-10-03T03:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T16:27:12.000Z","uid":121784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"82c1eb2fa8c2e8338e38dd2c23740134c84e7093","tid":2227680,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T03:47:03.000Z","msg":"【大曹石澗】<br />\n『位置』 大帽山<br />\n『方位』 源起大帽山西南 流入曹公潭<br />\n『難度』 ★★★<br />\n『土名』 不詳<br />\n在第一代九大石澗之中，「大帽山」獨佔三條，其為「大城」、「大玄」與「大曹石澗」，其中「大曹」應為三澗之中最綿長者，自下游「曹公潭」起至「荃錦公路」一段止，澗形極大，巨岩深潭兩者皆備，惟接近工業與寮屋區，水源已被污染，殊為可惜。公路以上村田一截澗道，水色稍清，而簾瀑短崖層降，景色秀美，有稱之為「小九寨溝」。踏上「川龍」之後向帽頂青年營一段的上游澗途，為精華所在，有多度的長瀑奔騰串連不休，令人暢快。<br />\n<br />\n(注意! 三星難度既澗, 比一般行山網站上既三星山徑難唔少, 風險亦較高. 另外此澗源頭既深且廣, 雨後山洪暴發風險較高.)<br />\n<br />\n交通: 由荃灣如心廣場, 坐51巴士, 於「新開田」站落車<br />\n<br />\n行入新開田村, 行無耐就到石橋, 橋下就係大曹石澗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3sLt18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3sLt18.jpg&h=195b7147&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢段太多水管又陰森, 再行上鐵盧城, 於廢屋旁先入澗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h2dZysd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh2dZysd.jpg&h=ab895077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一入澗就係小水壩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/prSGMPv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FprSGMPv.jpg&h=a2c61fb3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小潭小瀑不斷, 水清石潔<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wrCSTv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwrCSTv6.jpg&h=d6f17c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呢度玩下水消下暑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ziGXkd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FziGXkd0.jpg&h=cf4313fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n園林景色, 瀑布可正攀上<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gokk2sJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgokk2sJ.jpg&h=a26d3410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行左兩個半鐘左右, 到左分源位廣場<br />\n右源係正源, 可上到「大帽山瀑布」, 左邊係左源, 都可以接上大帽山道<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9afMX08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9afMX08.jpg&h=8b32df51&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n取左源<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/afE9VO8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FafE9VO8.jpg&h=f294186c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入左源後變為林澗, 瀑布仍不斷<br />\n旁邊都係泥坡好難上, 最安全既方法都係正攀瀑布<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNqJfPo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNqJfPo.jpg&h=605777d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瀑下有小彩虹<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQZU6V6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQZU6V6.jpg&h=6e2d4a59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n攀過一堆瀑後, 澗容變平淡小溪, 澗道雙分, 再取左支<br />\n發現不明物品, 應該離文明近了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i58R9as.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi58R9as.jpg&h=a2b514f4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去到源頭, 小支流不斷, 去到呢度應該係左源左左左左支 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OSxvFip.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOSxvFip.jpg&h=0d361252&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於無澗可循, 水源藏於泥土, 變為極為討厭既泥沼, 又污糟又多蚊<br />\n循絲帶, 車聲與人聲方向剷上草坡<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tkFtrZc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtkFtrZc.jpg&h=9546e70f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n約10分鐘後, 係呢度鑽返出康莊大道, 行幾步就到大帽山道軍閘, 返回文明世界<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPte6ZL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPte6ZL.jpg&h=9d7f121f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後, 沿車路就可以行返落出荃錦公路"},{"pid":"bbae4cf98ee1a14711787247513d1c8173fa2926","tid":2227680,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"又旺過旺角了"},{"pid":"295fb70fd5f1664a4942b5000cc1a3db050218ec","tid":2227680,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbae4cf98ee1a14711787247513d1c8173fa2926","tid":2227680,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"又旺過旺角了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:02:14.000Z","msg":"老少咸宜既郊遊徑先會旺, 澗線好難旺過旺角啦<br />\n唔係個個都鍾意行到全身濕哂水, 亦唔係個個都有能力手足並用攀爬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ded3fb7f3247f4754fecc0892da77720eeae79","tid":2227680,"uid":370202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"295fb70fd5f1664a4942b5000cc1a3db050218ec","tid":2227680,"uid":121784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bbae4cf98ee1a14711787247513d1c8173fa2926","tid":2227680,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T03:51:48.000Z","msg":"又旺過旺角了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T04:02:14.000Z","msg":"老少咸宜既郊遊徑先會旺, 澗線好難旺過旺角啦<br />\n唔係個個都鍾意行到全身濕哂水, 亦唔係個個都有能力手足並用攀爬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T16:27:12.000Z","msg":"見ig今年多左好多人行澗浸水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}